vernac_cmds: Fixpoint inc_dec_in_queue (s : Site) (q : queue Message) {struct q} : Prop := match q with | empty => False | input (inc_dec s2) q' => if eq_site_dec s2 s then True else False | input _ q' => inc_dec_in_queue s q' end.
Lemma inc_dec_in : forall (s : Site) (q : queue Message), inc_dec_in_queue s q -> In_queue Message (inc_dec s) q.
Lemma inc_dec_queue_equal : forall (q : queue Message) (s1 s2 : Site), inc_dec_in_queue s1 q -> inc_dec_in_queue s2 q -> s1 = s2.
Inductive parent : Site -> Site -> Prop := parent_intro : forall s1 s0 : Site, rt c0 s0 = true -> inc_dec_in_queue s1 (bm c0 s0 owner) -> parent s1 s0.
Inductive ancestor : Site -> Site -> Prop := | short : forall s1 s0 : Site, parent s1 s0 -> ancestor s1 s0 | long : forall s2 s1 s0 : Site, ancestor s2 s1 -> parent s1 s0 -> ancestor s2 s0.
Lemma decide_rt : forall s : Site, {rt c0 s = false} + {rt c0 s = true}.
Lemma decide_inc_dec_in_queue : forall s : Site, {s1 : Site | inc_dec_in_queue s1 (bm c0 s owner)} + {(forall s1 : Site, ~ inc_dec_in_queue s1 (bm c0 s owner))}.
Lemma decide_parent : forall s1 s3 : Site, {parent s1 s3} + {~ parent s1 s3}.
apply inc_dec_queue_equal with (q := bm c0 s2 owner).
Inductive direct_son : Site -> Prop := direct_son_intro : forall s : Site, s <> owner -> rt c0 s = true -> (forall s1 : Site, ~ inc_dec_in_queue s1 (bm c0 s owner)) -> direct_son s.
Inductive indirect_son1 : Site -> Prop := indirect_son1_intro : forall s : Site, s <> owner -> rt c0 s = true -> ~ (forall s1 : Site, ~ inc_dec_in_queue s1 (bm c0 s owner)) -> indirect_son1 s.
Inductive indirect_son2 : Site -> Prop := indirect_son2_intro : forall s s1 : Site, s <> owner /\ rt c0 s = true /\ direct_son s1 /\ ancestor s1 s -> indirect_son2 s.
Lemma decide_direct_son : forall s1 : Site, s1 <> owner -> {direct_son s1} + {~ direct_son s1}.
Lemma direct_or_indirect_son1 : forall s : Site, s <> owner -> rt c0 s = true -> {direct_son s} + {indirect_son1 s}.
Lemma disjoint_case_for_site : forall s : Site, {s = owner} + {rt c0 s = false} + {direct_son s} + {indirect_son1 s}.
Lemma ancestor_transitive : forall s1 s2 s3 : Site, ancestor s1 s2 -> ancestor s2 s3 -> ancestor s1 s3.
Lemma aux : forall s0 s1 s2 : Site, parent s0 s2 -> direct_son s0 -> ancestor s1 s2 -> s1 = s0.
apply inc_dec_queue_equal with (q := bm c0 s4 owner).
apply inc_dec_queue_equal with (q := bm c0 s5 owner).
Lemma decide_ancestor : forall x s s1 : Site, direct_son x -> ancestor x s -> indirect_son1 s1 -> (s1 = s \/ ancestor s1 s) \/ s1 <> s /\ ~ ancestor s1 s.
generalize (aux s0 s1 s2 H2 H3 H5).
apply inc_dec_queue_equal with (q := bm c0 s5 owner).
apply inc_dec_queue_equal with (q := bm c0 s6 owner).

Lemma inc_dec_in_post : forall (b : Bag_of_message) (s0 s1 s2 s3 : Site) (m : Message), inc_dec_in_queue s1 (b s0 owner) -> (forall s4 : Site, m <> inc_dec s4) -> inc_dec_in_queue s1 (Post_message Message m b s2 s3 s0 owner).

Lemma inc_dec_in_post2 : forall (b : Bag_of_message) (s0 s1 s2 s3 : Site) (m : Message), inc_dec_in_queue s1 (Post_message Message m b s2 s3 s0 owner) -> m <> inc_dec s1 -> inc_dec_in_queue s1 (b s0 owner).

Lemma inc_dec_not_in_post : forall (b : Bag_of_message) (s0 s1 s2 s3 : Site) (m : Message), ~ inc_dec_in_queue s1 (b s0 owner) -> (forall s4 : Site, m <> inc_dec s4) -> ~ inc_dec_in_queue s1 (Post_message Message m b s2 s3 s0 owner).
apply (inc_dec_in_post2 b s0 s1 s2 s3 m).

Lemma inc_dec_not_in_post2 : forall (b : Bag_of_message) (s0 s1 s2 s3 : Site) (m : Message), (forall s4 : Site, m <> inc_dec s4) -> ~ inc_dec_in_queue s1 (Post_message Message m b s2 s3 s0 owner) -> ~ inc_dec_in_queue s1 (b s0 owner).

Lemma inc_dec_not_in_first_out : forall (q : queue Message) (m : Message) (s3 : Site), first Message q = value Message m -> m <> inc_dec s3 -> ~ inc_dec_in_queue s3 q -> ~ inc_dec_in_queue s3 (first_out Message q).
intros m q1 H m0 s3 H0 H1.

Lemma inc_dec_in_first_out : forall (q : queue Message) (m : Message) (s3 : Site), first Message q = value Message m -> m <> inc_dec s3 -> inc_dec_in_queue s3 q -> inc_dec_in_queue s3 (first_out Message q).
intros m q1 H m0 s3 H0 H1.

Lemma inc_dec_not_in_collect : forall (b : Bag_of_message) (m : Message) (s0 s1 s2 s3 : Site), first Message (b s1 s2) = value Message m -> ~ inc_dec_in_queue s3 (b s0 owner) -> m <> inc_dec s3 -> ~ inc_dec_in_queue s3 (Collect_message Message b s1 s2 s0 owner).

Lemma inc_dec_in_collect : forall (b : Bag_of_message) (s0 s1 s2 s3 : Site) (m : Message), first Message (b s1 s2) = value Message m -> inc_dec_in_queue s3 (b s0 owner) -> m <> inc_dec s3 -> inc_dec_in_queue s3 (Collect_message Message b s1 s2 s0 owner).

Lemma inc_dec_in_collect2 : forall (b : Bag_of_message) (m : Message) (s0 s1 s2 s3 : Site), first Message (b s1 s2) = value Message m -> inc_dec_in_queue s3 (Collect_message Message b s1 s2 s0 owner) -> inc_dec_in_queue s3 (b s0 owner).
intros b m s0 s1 s2 s3 H.
Lemma not_inc_dec_in : forall q : queue Message, (forall s : Site, ~ inc_dec_in_queue s q) -> forall s : Site, ~ In_queue Message (inc_dec s) q.
Lemma joining_node : forall (c : Config) (s2 : Site), legal c -> rt c s2 = false -> forall s3 s4 : Site, parent c s3 s4 -> s2 <> s3.

Lemma ancestor_does_not_join : forall (c0 : Config) (s2 s3 s4 : Site), legal c0 -> legal (rec_copy2_trans c0 s2) -> ancestor (rec_copy2_trans c0 s2) s3 s4 -> rt c0 s2 = false -> first Message (bm c0 owner s2) = value Message copy -> s3 <> s2.

Lemma parent_does_not_join2 : forall (c0 : Config) (s1 s2 s3 s4 : Site), legal c0 -> legal (rec_copy3_trans c0 s1 s2) -> parent (rec_copy3_trans c0 s1 s2) s3 s4 -> rt c0 s2 = false -> first Message (bm c0 s1 s2) = value Message copy -> s3 <> s2.

generalize (positive_st (rec_copy3_trans c0 s1 s2) s0 s5 H8 H0 H6).
generalize (st_rt (rec_copy3_trans c0 s1 s2) s0 H0 H8 H9).

generalize (st_rt c0 s0 H H8 H15).
